folder: Henley Road & Chevy Chase Street, Queens, NY
original_title: Queens: Henley Road - Chevy Chase Street
text:
Henley Road, at Chevy Chase Street, showing, in different directions, the wooded area lying between Henley Road and Grand Central Parkway. View 1 is west on Henley Road,and
view 2 is east.
March 25, 1932
Views 1,2,3
P. L. Sperr
